"(\"<literal>/usr/share/doc/linux-doc-2.6.*/Documentation/filesystems/*</"
"literal>\") provided by the <literal>linux-doc-2.6.*</literal> package."
msgstr ""
"Veja \"<literal>proc.txt(.gz)</literal>\", \"<literal>sysfs.txt(.gz)</"
"literal>\" e outros documentos relacionados na documentação do kernel Linux "
"(\"<literal>/usr/share/doc/linux-doc-2.6.*/Documentation/filesystems/*</"
"literal>\") disponibilizados pelo pacote <literal>linux-doc-2.6.*</literal>."

