msgstr ""
"<literal>pcregrep</literal>(1) do pacote <literal>pcregrep</literal> "
"corresponde texto com padrões <ulink url=\"&perlcompatiblererexpressionspcre;"
"\">Perl Compatible Regular Expressions (PCRE)</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"<literal>python</literal>(1) with the <literal>re</literal> module can do "
