#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The integrity of the top level \"<literal>Release</literal>\" file is "
"verified by cryptographic infrastructure called the <ulink url=\"&secureapt;"
"\">secure apt</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"A integridade do ficheiro \"<literal>Release</literal>\" de nível de topo é "
"verificada ela infraestrutura criptográfica chamada <ulink url=\"&secureapt;"
"\">secure apt</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"The cryptographic signature file \"<literal>Release.gpg</literal>\" is "
"created from the authentic top level \"<literal>Release</literal>\" file and "
"the secret Debian archive key."
msgstr ""
"O ficheiro de assinatura criptográfica \"<literal>Release.gpg</literal>\" é "
"criado a partir do ficheiro \"<literal>Release</literal>\" de nível de topo "
"autenticado e a chave de arquivo Debian secreta."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"The public Debian archive key can be seeded into \"<literal>/etc/apt/trusted."
"gpg</literal>\";"
msgstr ""
"A chave do arquivo Debian público pode ser semeada em \"<literal>/etc/apt/"
"trusted.gpg</literal>\";"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"automatically by installing the keyring with the latest <literal>base-files</"
"literal> package, or"
msgstr ""
"automaticamente ao instalar o chaveiro com o pacote <literal>base-files</"
"literal> mais recente, ou"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"manually by <literal>gpg</literal> or <literal>apt-key</literal> tool with "
"<ulink url=\"&thelatestpublicapmasterdebianorg;\">the latest public archive "
"key posted on the ftp-master.debian.org</ulink> ."
msgstr ""
"manualmente pela ferramenta <literal>gpg</literal> ou <literal>apt-key</"
"literal> com <ulink url=\"&thelatestpublicapmasterdebianorg;\">a chave de "
"arquivo público mais recente publicada em ftp-master.debian.org</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">secure APT</emphasis> system verifies the "
"integrity of the downloaded top level \"<literal>Release</literal>\" file "
"cryptographically by this \"<literal>Release.gpg</literal>\" file and the "
"public Debian archive key in \"<literal>/etc/apt/trusted.gpg</literal>\"."
msgstr ""
"O sistema <emphasis role=\"strong\">secure APT</emphasis> verifica a "
"integridade do ficheiro \"<literal>Release</literal>\" de nível de topo "
"descarregado criptograficamente por este ficheiro \"<literal>Release.gpg</"
"literal>\" a pela chave de arquivo público Debian em \"<literal>/etc/apt/"
"trusted.gpg</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The integrity of all the \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" and "
"\"<literal>Sources</literal>\" files are verified by using MD5sum values in "
"its top level \"<literal>Release</literal>\" file.  The integrity of all "
"package files are verified by using MD5sum values in the "
"\"<literal>Packages</literal>\" and \"<literal>Sources</literal>\" files.  "
"See <literal>debsums</literal>(1) and <xref linkend="
"\"_verification_of_installed_package_files\"/>."
msgstr ""
"A integridade de todos os ficheiros \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" e "
"\"<literal>Sources</literal>\" é verificada usando valores MD5sum no seu "
"ficheiro \"<literal>Release</literal>\" de nível de topo. A integridade de "
"todos os ficheiros de pacotes é verificada usando valores MD5sum nos "
"ficheiros \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" e \"<literal>Sources</literal>\" "
"Veja <literal>debsums</literal>(1) e <xref linkend="
"\"_verification_of_installed_package_files\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Since the cryptographic signature verification is very CPU intensive process "
"than the MD5sum value calculation, use of MD5sum value for each package "
"while using cryptographic signature for the top level \"<literal>Release</"
"literal>\" file provides <ulink url=\"&thegoodsecuritywththeperformance;"
"\">the good security with the performance</ulink> (see <xref linkend="
"\"_data_security_infrastructure\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Como a verificação de assinatura criptográfica é um processo muito mais "
"intenso para a CPU que o cálculo de valores MD5sum, o uso de valores MD5sum "
"para cada pacote enquanto se usa assinatura criptográfica para o ficheiro "
"\"<literal>Release</literal>\" de nível de topo disponibiliza <ulink url="
"\"&thegoodsecuritywththeperformance;\">a boa segurança com a performance</"
"ulink> (veja <xref linkend=\"_data_security_infrastructure\"/>)."

