#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"First 4 types of files are shared by all the pertinent APT commands and "
"updated from command line by \"<literal>apt-get update</literal>\" and "
"\"<literal>aptitude update</literal>\".  The \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" "
"meta data are updated if there is the \"<literal>deb</literal>\" line in "
"\"<literal>/etc/apt/sources.list</literal>\". The \"<literal>Sources</"
"literal>\" meta data are updated if there is the \"<literal>deb-src</literal>"
"\" line in \"<literal>/etc/apt/sources.list</literal>\"."
msgstr ""
"Os primeiros 4 tipos de ficheiros são partilhados por todos os comandos APT "
"pertinentes e actualizados a partir da linha de comandos pelo \"<literal>apt-"
"get update</literal>\" e \"<literal>aptitude update</literal>\". Os meta "
"dados \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" são actualizados se existir a linha "
"\"<literal>deb</literal>\" em \"<literal>/etc/apt/sources.list</literal>\". "
"Os meta dados \"<literal>Sources</literal>\" são actualizados se existir a "
"linha \"<literal>deb-src</literal>\" em \"<literal>/etc/apt/sources.list</"
"literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" and \"<literal>Sources</literal>\" meta "
"data contain \"<literal>Filename:</literal>\" stanza pointing to the file "
"location of the binary and source packages.  Currently, these packages are "
"located under the \"<literal>pool/</literal>\" directory tree for the "
"improved transition over the releases."
msgstr ""
"Os meta dados \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" e \"<literal>Sources</literal>"
"\" contêm a estrofe \"<literal>Filename:</literal>\" que aponta para a "
"localização de ficheiro dos pacotes binários e fonte. Actualmente, estes "
"pacotes são localizados sob a árvore de directórios \"<literal>pool/</"
"literal>\" para a transição melhorada sobre os lançamentos."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Local copies of \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" meta data can be "
"interactively searched with the help of <literal>aptitude</literal>.  The "
"specialized search command <literal>grep-dctrl</literal>(1) can search local "
"copies of \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" and \"<literal>Sources</literal>\" "
"meta data."
msgstr ""
"As cópias locais dos meta dados \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" podem ser "
"pesquisadas interactivamente coma ajuda do <literal>aptitude</literal>. O "
"comando de procura especializada <literal>grep-dctrl</literal>(1) pode "
"pesquisar as cópias locais dos meta dados \"<literal>Packages</literal>\" e "
"\"<literal>Sources</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Local copy of \"<literal>Contents-&lt;architecture&gt;</literal>\" meta data "
"can be updated by \"<literal>apt-file update</literal>\" and its location is "
