"Isto existe sempre no ficheiro \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>"
"\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "The network interface served by the DHCP"
msgstr "A interface de rede servida por DHCP"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"After prepairing the system by <xref linkend="
"\"_the_dhcp_connection_with_the_ethernet\"/>, the network interface served "
"by the DHCP is configured by creating the configuration entry in the "
"\"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file as the following."
msgstr ""
"Após preparar o sistema por <xref linkend="
"\"_the_dhcp_connection_with_the_ethernet\"/>, a interface de rede servida "
"por DHCP é configurada ao criar a entrada de configuração no ficheiro "
"\"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" como o seguinte."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"allow-hotplug eth0\n"
"iface eth0 inet dhcp\n"
" hostname \"mymachine\""
msgstr ""
"allow-hotplug eth0\n"
"iface eth0 inet dhcp\n"
" hostname \"minha_máquina\""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"When the Linux kernel detects the physical interface <literal>eth0</"
"literal>, the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>allow-hotplug</literal></"
"emphasis> stanza causes <literal>ifup</literal> to bring up the interface "
"and the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> stanza "
"causes <literal>ifup</literal> to use DHCP to configure the interface."
msgstr ""
"Quando o kernel Linux detecta a interface física <literal>eth0</literal>, a "
"estrofe <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>allow-hotplug</literal></"
"emphasis> faz com que <literal>ifup</literal> active a interface e a estrofe "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> faz com que "
"<literal>ifup</literal> use DHCP para configurar a interface."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "The network interface with the static IP"
msgstr "A interface de rede com IP estático"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The network interface served by the static IP is configured by creating the "
"configuration entry in the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" "
"file as the following."
