"and the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> stanza "
"causes <literal>ifup</literal> to use the static IP to configure the "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Quando o kernel Linux detecta a interface física <literal>eth0</literal>, a "
"estrofe <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>allow-hotplug</literal></"
"emphasis> faz com que <literal>ifup</literal> active a interface e a estrofe "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> faz com que "
"<literal>ifup</literal> use IP estático para configurar a interface."

