"value for the corresponding option under the <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis> stanza"
msgstr ""
"valor para a opção correspondente sob a estrofe <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>iface</literal></emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Here, each environment variable, \"<literal>$IF_&lt;OPTION&gt;</literal>\", "
"is created from the name for the corresponding option such as &lt;"
"option1&gt; and &lt;option2&gt; by prepending \"<literal>$IF_</literal>\", "
"converting the case to the upper case, replacing hyphens to underscores, and "
"discarding non-alphanumeric characters."
msgstr ""
"Aqui, cada variável de ambiente, \"<literal>$IF_&lt;OPTION&gt;</literal>\", "
"é criada a partir do nome da opção correspondente tal como &lt;opção1&gt; e "
"&lt;opção2&gt; ao preceder \"<literal>$IF_</literal>\", convertendo para "
"maiúsculas,substituindo os hífens por underscores, e descartando os "
"caracteres não-alfanuméricos."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><para>
msgid ""
"See <xref linkend=\"_the_basic_syntax_of_etc_network_interfaces\"/> for &lt;"
"address_family&gt;, &lt;method_name&gt;, &lt;option1&gt; and &lt;option2&gt;."
msgstr ""
"Veja <xref linkend=\"_the_basic_syntax_of_etc_network_interfaces\"/> para "
"&lt;família_de_endereços&gt;, &lt;nome_de_método&gt;, &lt;opção1&gt; e &lt;"
"opção2&gt;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The <literal>ifupdown-extra</literal> package (see <xref linkend="
"\"_the_ifupdown_extra_package\"/>) uses these environment variables to "
"extend the functionality of the <literal>ifupdown</literal> package.  The "
"<literal>ifmetric</literal> package (see <xref linkend="
"\"_the_ifmetric_package\"/>) installs the \"<literal>/etc/network/if-up.d/"
"ifmetric</literal>\" script which sets the metric via the \"<literal>"
"$IF_METRIC</literal>\" variable.  The <literal>guessnet</literal> package "
"(see <xref linkend=\"_mapping_with_guessnet\"/>), which provides simple and "
"powerful framework for the auto-selection of the network configuration via "
"the mapping mechanism, also uses these."
msgstr ""
"O pacote <literal>ifupdown-extra</literal> (veja <xref linkend="
"\"_the_ifupdown_extra_package\"/>) usa estas variáveis de ambiente para "
"estender a funcionalidade do pacote <literal>ifupdown</literal>. O pacote "
"<literal>ifmetric</literal> (veja <xref linkend=\"_the_ifmetric_package\"/>) "
"instala o script \"<literal>/etc/network/if-up.d/ifmetric</literal>\" o qual "
"define a métrica via variável \"<literal>$IF_METRIC</literal>\". O pacote "
"<literal>guessnet</literal> (veja <xref linkend=\"_mapping_with_guessnet\"/"
">), que disponibiliza um estrutura simples e poderosa para a selecção "
"automática da configuração de rede via o mecanismo de mapeamento, também as "
"usa."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><para>
msgid ""
"For more specific examples of custom network configuration scripts using "
"these environment variables, you should check example scripts in \"<literal>/"
"usr/share/doc/ifupdown/examples/*</literal>\" and scripts used in "
"<literal>ifscheme</literal> and <literal>ifupdown-scripts-zg2</literal> "
"packages.  These additional scripts have some overlaps of functionalities "
"with basic <literal>ifupdown-extra</literal> and <literal>guessnet</literal> "
"packages.  If you install these additional scripts, you should customize "
"these scripts to avoid interferences."
msgstr ""
"Para exemplos mais específicos de scripts personalizados de configuração de "
"rede que usam estas variáveis de ambiente, você deve consultar os scripts "
"exemplo em \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/ifupdown/examples/*</literal>\" e os "
"scripts usados nos pacotes <literal>ifscheme</literal> e <literal>ifupdown-"
"scripts-zg2</literal>. Estes scripts adicionais têm algumas sobreposições de "
"funcionalidades com os pacotes básicos <literal>ifupdown-extra</literal> e "
"<literal>guessnet</literal>. Se você instalar estes scripts adicionais, deve "
"personalizar estes scripts para evitar interferências."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "Mapping with guessnet"
msgstr "Mapeando com guessnet"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Instead of manually choosing configuration as described in <xref linkend="
"\"_the_manually_switchable_network_configuration\"/>, you can use the "
"mapping mechanism described in <xref linkend=\"_the_mapping_stanza\"/> to "
"select network configuration automatically with custom scripts."
msgstr ""
"Em vez de escolher manualmente a configuração como descrito em <xref linkend="
"\"_the_manually_switchable_network_configuration\"/>, você pode usar o "
"mecanismo de mapeamento descrito em <xref linkend=\"_the_mapping_stanza\"/> "
"para seleccionar automaticamente a configuração de rede com scripts "
"personalizados."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8) command provided by the "
"<literal>guessnet</literal> package is designed to be used as a mapping "
"script and provides powerful framework to enhance the <literal>ifupdown</"
"literal> system."
msgstr ""
"O comando <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8) disponibilizado pelo "
"pacote <literal>guessnet</literal> foi desenhado para ser usado como um "
"script de mapeamento e disponibiliza uma estrutura poderosa para melhorar o "
"sistema <literal>ifupdown</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"You list test condition as the value for <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> options for each network "
"configuration under <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></"
"emphasis> stanza."
msgstr ""
"Você listas as condições de teste como o valor para as opções do <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> para cada "
"configuração de rede sob a estrofe <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</"
"literal></emphasis>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"Mapping choses the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></"
"emphasis> with first non-ERROR result as the network configuration."
msgstr ""
"O mapeamento escolhe a <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>iface</literal></"
"emphasis> com o primeiro resultado não-ERRO como a configuração de rede."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"This dual usage of the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file "
"by the mapping script, <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>, and the "
"original network configuration infrastructure, <literal>ifupdown</literal>, "
"does not cause negative impacts since <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> options only export extra "
"environment variables to scripts run by the <literal>ifupdown</literal> "
"system.  See details in <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8)."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilização dupla do ficheiro \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</"
"literal>\" pelo script de mapeamento, <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>, "
"e a infraestrutura original de configuração de rede, <literal>ifupdown</"
"literal>, não causa impactos negativos porque as opções do <emphasis role="
"\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> apenas exportam variáveis "
"de ambiente extras para scripts executados pelo sistema <literal>ifupdown</"
"literal>. Veja detalhes em <literal>guessnet-ifupdown</literal>(8)."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><para>
msgid ""
"When multiple <emphasis role=\"strong\"><literal>guessnet</literal></"
"emphasis> option lines are required in \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</"
"literal>\", use option lines started with <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet1</literal></emphasis>, <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet2</literal></emphasis>, and so on, since the "
"<literal>ifupdown</literal> package does not allow starting strings of "
"option lines to be repeated."
msgstr ""
"Quando são necessárias múltiplas linhas de opção <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet</literal></emphasis> em \"<literal>/etc/network/"
"interfaces</literal>\", use linhas de opção começadas com <emphasis role="
"\"strong\"><literal>guessnet1</literal></emphasis>, <emphasis role=\"strong"
"\"><literal>guessnet2</literal></emphasis>, e assim em diante, porque o "
"pacote <literal>ifupdown</literal> não permite que as strings de inicio das "
"linhas de opção sejam repetidas."

