msgstr ""
"Este processo e a descoberta do <ulink url=\"&pathmtupmtudiscovery;"
"\">Caminho MTU (PMTU)</ulink> (<ulink url=\"&rfcbbjb;\">RFC1191</ulink>) e o "
"comando <literal>tracepath</literal>(8) automatiza isto."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><para>
msgid ""
