"bandwidth, <literal>mailfilter</literal> or <literal>mpop</literal> may be "
"useful.  Whichever mail retriever utilities are used, it is good idea to "
"configure system to deliver retrieved mails to MDA, such as "
"<literal>maildrop</literal>, via pipe."
