msgstr "Carregue em ^D (CTRL-D) para terminar a sessão do ssh-agent."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"For the X server, the normal Debian startup script executes <literal>ssh-"
"agent</literal> as the parent process.  So you only need to execute "
"<literal>ssh-add</literal> once. For more, read <literal>ssh-agent</literal>"
"(1)and <literal>ssh-add</literal>(1)."
msgstr ""
"Para o servidor X, o script de arranque normal de Debian executa o "
"<literal>ssh-agent</literal> como o processo pai. Portanto você apenas "
"precisa de executar o <literal>ssh-add</literal> uma vez. Para mais, leia "
"<literal>ssh-agent</literal>(1) e <literal>ssh-add</literal>(1)."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "How to shutdown the remote system on SSH"
msgstr "Como desligar o sistema remoto em SSH"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"You need to protect the process doing \"<literal>shutdown -h now</literal>"
"\" (see <xref linkend=\"_how_to_shutdown_the_system\"/>) from the "
"termination of SSH using the <literal>at</literal>(1) command (see <xref "
"linkend=\"_scheduling_tasks_once\"/>) by the following."
msgstr ""
"Você precisa de proteger o processo ao fazer \"<literal>shutdown -h now</"
"literal>\" (veja <xref linkend=\"_how_to_shutdown_the_system\"/>) a partir "
"da terminação do SSH usando o comando <literal>at</literal>(1) (veja <xref "
"linkend=\"_scheduling_tasks_once\"/>) com o seguinte."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "# echo \"shutdown -h now\" | at now"
msgstr "# echo \"shutdown -h now\" | at now"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Running \"<literal>shutdown -h now</literal>\" in <literal>screen</literal>"
"(1) (see <xref linkend=\"_the_screen_program\"/>) session is another way to "
