#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "Recording the shell activities cleanly"
msgstr "Gravar as actividades da shell de modo limpo"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The simple use of <literal>script</literal>(1) (see <xref linkend="
"\"_recording_the_shell_activities\"/>) to record shell activity produces a "
"file with control characters.  This can be avoided by using <literal>col</"
"literal>(1) as the following."
msgstr ""
"O uso simples de <literal>script</literal>(1) (veja <xref linkend="
"\"_recording_the_shell_activities\"/>) para gravar a actividade da shell "
"produz um ficheiro com caracteres de controle. Isto pode ser evitado ao usar "
"o <literal>col</literal>(1) como o seguinte."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Do whatever … and press <literal>Ctrl-D</literal> to exit <literal>script</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Faça o que tem a fazer ... e carregue em <literal>Ctrl-D</literal> para "
"terminar o <literal>script</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ col -bx &lt;typescript &gt;cleanedfile\n"
"$ vim cleanedfile"
msgstr ""
"$ col -bx &lt;typescript &gt;ficheiro_limpo\n"
"$ vim ficheiro_limpo"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"If you don't have <literal>script</literal> (for example, during the boot "
"process in the initramfs), you can use following instead."
msgstr ""
"Se você não tem o <literal>script</literal> (por exemplo, durante o processo "
"de arranque no initramfs), então use antes o seguinte."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ sh -i 2&gt;&amp;1 | tee typescript"
msgstr "$ sh -i 2&gt;&amp;1 | tee typescript"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><para>
msgid ""
"Some <literal>x-terminal-emulator</literal> such as <literal>gnome-terminal</"
"literal> can record.  You may wish to extend line buffer for scrollback."
