#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
msgid "Debugging the Debian package"
msgstr "Depurar o pacote Debian"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Since all installed binaries should be stripped on the Debian system by "
"default, most debugging symbols are removed in the normal package.  In order "
"to debug Debian packages with <literal>gdb</literal>(1), corresponding "
"<literal>*-dbg</literal> packages need to be installed (e.g. <literal>libc6-"
"dbg</literal> in the case of <literal>libc6</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"Como todos os binários instalados devem estar despidos no sistema Debian por "
"predefinição, a maioria dos símbolos de depuração são removidos no pacote "
"normal. De modo a depurar pacotes Debian com o <literal>gdb</literal>(1), os "
"pacotes <literal>*-dbg</literal> correspondentes precisam de ser instalados "
"(ex. <literal>libc6-dbg</literal> no caso do <literal>libc6</literal>)."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"If a package to be debugged does not provide its <literal>*-dbg</literal> "
"package, you need to install it after rebuilding it by the following."
msgstr ""
"Se um pacote a ser depurado não disponibiliza o seu pacote <literal>*-dbg</"
"literal>, você precisa de instalá-lo após o reconstruir com o seguinte."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"$ mkdir /path/new ; cd /path/new\n"
"$ sudo apt-get update\n"
"$ sudo apt-get dist-upgrade\n"
"$ sudo apt-get install fakeroot devscripts build-essential\n"
"$ sudo apt-get build-dep source_package_name\n"
"$ apt-get source package_name\n"
"$ cd package_name*"
msgstr ""
"$ mkdir /path/new ; cd /path/new\n"
"$ sudo apt-get update\n"
"$ sudo apt-get dist-upgrade\n"
"$ sudo apt-get install fakeroot devscripts build-essential\n"
"$ sudo apt-get build-dep nome_do_pacote_fonte\n"
"$ apt-get source nome_do_pacote\n"
"$ cd nome_do_pacote*"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid "Fix bugs if needed."
msgstr "Corrigir bugs se necessário"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
